name: UGO
description: Gooo - UGO - WeGo ecosystem is a platform rewards users for performing their primary job, above and beyond the standard salary. Users turn ON the app while performing their primary job to EARN Gooo points, which can be easily exchanged for physical products (Phase 1) or converted to UGO tokens (Phase 2). After the Gooo App and the UGO token, WeGo emerges as the THIRD phase to completely support users in the realms of Cryptocurrency and Global Finance by providing Neo-bank services, Multi-Crypto Wallet, Worldwide Debit Card, Retail and ATM Usage.
